title: [Galinroe's Weaponry]
description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A gilded maple table and a plain wooden table sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on an unfinished wooden floor.

Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A gilded maple table and a wide knotted oak counter sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on an unfinished wooden floor.
